descriptionHTML:
★Requires Android 5.0 (L) on your watch★

Ever feel like the year is over before you know it? Keep track of it with this watchface! The main dial takes a year to make a full rotation!

Features configurable:
- Year dial color
- Background
- Time style (digital, analog, none)
- Digital text color



Icon credits: http://icons8.com/
comments: For phone Any chance you could make this available for a phone lockscreen?
